description: The First High School Extracurricular Activities Federation is one of the three most important student organizations in http://anidb.net/ch67045 [First High School], alongside the http://anidb.net/ch67046 [Student Council] and the http://anidb.net/ch67047 [Disciplinary Committee]. The Federation`s job is to supervise all extracurricular activities First High students take part in. It also assigns three of the nine members of the Disciplinary Committee.
name: Kokuritsu Mahou Daigaku Fuzoku Daiichi Koutougakkou Bukatsu Ren
